org.pepstock.charba.client.resources

Class AbstractInjectableResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.resources.AbstractInjectableResource
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnnotationPluginResource, ChartJsResource, DataLabelsPluginResource, EmptyResource, GeoControllerResource, InjectableTextResource, JsHelperResource, LabelsPluginResource, LuxonAdapterResource, LuxonLibraryResource, TreeMapControllerResource, ZoomPluginHammerResource, ZoomPluginResource

    public abstract class AbstractInjectableResource
extends Object
    Defines an object which must inject script or CSS style objects in the DOM document, at runtime.
    It must have a name and should be a unique value because it will be used to set the element (script or style) id.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
